<L>__{exterior yacht on deck night}
<A>__{milo's yacht is anchored about a half mile offshore. island lights blink in the distance. fog rolls in. milo emerges from the cabin onto the deck. crosses to the railing, looks down at:}
<B>__{fishing boat}
<A>__{bobbing in the water about thirty yards away. a fisherman is waving his arms. hailing them. beside him, his wife and seventeen year old son.}
<C>__{fisherman}
<D>__{hey! buddy, i got a cracked engine casing, i'm dead in the water! can i get a tow?}
<A>__{milo swears under his breath. calls out:}
<C>__{milo}
<D>__{i'm sorry, sir. this boat is island security, we're under strict orders to stay within this sector.}
<C>__{fisherman}
<D>__{aw, shit! look, it'll take ten minutes!}
<C>__{milo}
<D>__{i'm sorry, we can't help you.}
<C>__{fisherman}
<D>__{goddammit, now i gotta call the coast guard!}
<A>__{milo's crewman steps up to the rail. speaks urgently:}
<C>__{crew member}
<D>__{milo, he's gonna bring the coast guard down on top of us.}
<A>__{milo ponders for maybe three seconds. then he calls out:}
<C>__{milo}
<D>__{excuse me. sir?}
<A>__{the fisherman turns. his family beside him.}
<C>__{milo}
<D>__{fuck you, sir.}
<A>__{he reaches under his windbreaker. pulls out an ingram model machine gun.}
<B>__{opens fire.}
<A>__{the entire family is blown away. wood splingers pop and fly.}
<B>__{glass shatters.}
<A>__{the bodies topple like broken toys. milo ceases fire. turns to his crewman.}
<C>__{milo}
<D>__{problem solved. get over there and put the bodies below where they can't be seen.}
<A>__{he saunters away as if nothing unusual has occurred.}
